title: #16 - CouRage and Nadeshot Tease 100 Thieves’ BRAND NEW Content House ft. Valkyrae and BrookeAB
itunes:title: #16 - CouRage and Nadeshot Tease 100 Thieves’ BRAND NEW Content House ft. Valkyrae and BrookeAB
description: On the premiere episode of the second season of The CouRage and Nadeshot Show presented by Cash App, CouRage and Nadeshot welcome on fellow 100 Thieves content creators BrookeAB and Valkyrae. They tease details of the new content house, the Half A Million Halftime Show, addiction to Escape From Tarkhov, the coronavirus epidemic, and more.
